659
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:29,997
<i>Ooh, it got cold in here.</i>

660
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,296
<i>Mom,</i>

661
00:37:39,298 --> 00:37:42,093
<i>I don't know if I can still</i>
<i>continue living here</i>

662
00:37:43,344 --> 00:37:46,013
<i>after all the trouble</i>
<i>I've caused in this house.</i>

663
00:37:48,766 --> 00:37:51,352
<i>[Maxim] Macy, don't do this</i>
<i>for the sake of our children!</i>

664
00:37:56,399 --> 00:37:58,651
<i>-Elle. Elle?</i>
<i>-[Elle sobbing]</i>

665
00:37:58,734 --> 00:38:00,194
<i>Elle. Wait.</i>

666
00:38:00,278 --> 00:38:02,405
<i>Hold on, Elle.</i>

667
00:38:05,283 --> 00:38:06,492
<i>What's happening?</i>

668
00:38:07,118 --> 00:38:11,247
<i>Mom, Rill, and I</i>
<i>are moving out temporarily.</i>

669
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:12,456
<i>[Elle sniffles]</i>

670
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:15,293
<i>Max, about what happened…</i>

671
00:38:16,168 --> 00:38:18,212
<i>I know you're mad at me.</i>

672
00:38:18,838 --> 00:38:20,715
<i>So all this time,</i>

673
00:38:22,967 --> 00:38:25,344
<i>you were just pretending</i>
<i>that we were okay--</i>

674
00:38:25,428 --> 00:38:30,808
<i>In the beginning. Because I was so afraid.</i>

675
00:38:30,891 --> 00:38:33,185
<i>I was so scared.</i>

676
00:38:34,103 --> 00:38:36,230
<i>Is that why you became nice to me, Elle?</i>

677
00:38:37,189 --> 00:38:40,401
<i>Not all of it was fake, Max.</i>

678
00:38:41,068 --> 00:38:45,031
<i>I saw the goodness in you, I saw it.</i>

679
00:38:45,114 --> 00:38:49,827
<i>I saw that you had no intention</i>
<i>of ruining this family.</i>

680
00:38:49,910 --> 00:38:53,456
<i>At the end of the day,</i>

681
00:38:53,539 --> 00:38:57,043
<i>it was me who ruined our family.</i>

682
00:38:57,126 --> 00:39:00,296
<i>I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.</i>

683
00:39:00,379 --> 00:39:02,590
<i>I know that you won't forgive me.</i>

684
00:39:02,673 --> 00:39:05,092
<i>But still, I'm so sorry.</i>

685
00:39:07,178 --> 00:39:09,597
<i>-Macy.</i>
<i>-Maxim, you know my terms.</i>

686
00:39:10,556 --> 00:39:12,892
<i>Elle, dear, let's go.</i>

687
00:39:12,975 --> 00:39:14,685
<i>[Macy] Maxrill is in the car.</i>

688
00:39:18,147 --> 00:39:19,648
<i>Sorry, Max.</i>

689
00:39:23,694 --> 00:39:24,904
<i>[Elle] I'm sorry, Dad. [sobs]</i>

690
00:39:29,200 --> 00:39:30,868
<i>You're just like your mother.</i>

691
00:39:32,244 --> 00:39:34,038
<i>You're a troublemaker.</i>

692
00:39:38,459 --> 00:39:39,460
<i>[Macy] Let's go, Elle.</i>

693
00:39:45,091 --> 00:39:48,552
<i>[Max sobbing]</i>

694
00:39:51,847 --> 00:39:53,224
<i>I'm sorry, Dad.</i>

695
00:39:54,892 --> 00:39:56,018
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

696
00:40:03,317 --> 00:40:06,404
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

697
00:40:09,949 --> 00:40:13,035
