698
00:40:31,846 --> 00:40:33,806
<i>♪ He's into her… ♪</i>

699
00:40:33,889 --> 00:40:35,391
<i>She's cheating on Deib.</i>

700
00:40:35,474 --> 00:40:37,810
<i>[Kim] </i>Deib is gonna be so pissed!

701
00:40:37,893 --> 00:40:41,105
<i>-[Deib] Why would I be jealous of the guy?</i>
<i>-C'mon. You're jealous.</i>

702
00:40:41,188 --> 00:40:43,607
<i>-Did you have another girlfriend?</i>
<i>-I stayed faithful to you.</i>

703
00:40:44,316 --> 00:40:46,402
<i>I promise you</i>
<i>that I won't leave you again.</i>

704
00:40:46,986 --> 00:40:50,531
<i>Deib, you don't have to pretend</i>
<i>that you're brave.</i>

705
00:40:50,614 --> 00:40:54,535
<i>Even the brave cry,</i>
<i>but they never give up.</i>

706
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,537
<i>Max?</i>

